('Sinigang na Baboy', 'A sour and savory soup made with pork and tamarind.', 'Pork belly, Tamarind base, Kangkong, Radish, Tomato.', 'Boil pork until tender. Add tamarind mix. Add vegetables last.', 'https://asianinspirations.com.au/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/R02988-Pork-Sinigang.jpg'),
