('Bibingka', 'Traditional Filipino rice cake.', 'Rice flour, Coconut milk, Sugar, Eggs, Grated coconut.', 'Mix ingredients. Pour into banana leaf-lined molds. Bake until set.', 'https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/7/7e/Bibingka-6.jpg/960px-Bibingka-6.jpg'),
('Lumpiang Shanghai', 'Filipino-style spring rolls with ground pork filling.', 'Ground pork, Carrot, Onion, Garlic, Spring roll wrappers.', 'Mix filling ingredients. Wrap in spring roll wrappers. Deep fry until golden.', 'https://themayakitchen.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/LUMPIANG-SHANGHAI.jpg'),
