('Turon', 'Fried banana spring rolls with caramelized sugar.', 'Saba bananas, Brown sugar, Spring roll wrappers, Oil for frying.', 'Wrap banana slices with brown sugar in spring roll wrappers. Fry until golden.', 'https://themayakitchen.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/TURON.jpg'),
('Puto', 'Steamed rice cakes, often served as a side dish.', 'Rice flour, Sugar, Baking powder, Coconut milk, Cheese (optional).', 'Mix ingredients. Pour into molds. Steam until cooked.', 'https://flouredframe.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/filipino-puto-15.jpg'),
('Patatim', 'A Filipino-Chinese braised pork hock dish slow-cooked until very tender in a savory-sweet sauce.', 'Pork, Soy sauce, Star anise, laurel, pepper, garlic, onions, brown sugar', 'Marinate pork. Sear until brown. Simmer with spices and sauce until tender.', 'https://delivery.vikings.ph/cdn/shop/products/PataTimWhole_0b8887e1-e0c5-43da-9a11-7bba479c982a_800x.jpg?v=1600093113'),
('Empanada', 'A stuffed bread or pastry baked or fried.', 'Flour, Ground meat, Potatoes, Carrots, Onions, Spices.', 'Prepare dough. Cook filling. Assemble and bake or fry until golden brown.', 'https://cdn-ilddihb.nitrocdn.com/MgqZCGPEMHvMRLsisMUCAIMWvgGMxqaj/assets/images/optimized/rev-e5c3642/www.goya.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/empanadas-beef-turnovers.jpg'),
('Callos', 'A Spanish-influenced Filipino stew made with tripe, chickpeas, and chorizo.', 'Beef tripe, Chickpeas, Chorizo, Tomato sauce, Bell peppers.', 'Boil tripe until tender. Sauté chorizo and vegetables. Simmer with tripe and sauce.', 'https://www.simpol.ph/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/CALLOS.jpg'),
('Arroz Caldo', 'A comforting Filipino rice porridge flavored with ginger and garlic.', 'Rice, Chicken, Ginger, Garlic, Fish sauce, Green onions.', 'Sauté garlic and ginger. Add chicken and rice. Simmer until rice is soft. Garnish with green onions.', 'https://www.eatwithcarmen.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Arroz-Caldo-with-Chicken.jpg'),
