('Pancit Malabon', 'A Filipino noodle dish known for its thick rice noodles and seafood toppings.', 'Thick rice noodles, Shrimp, Squid, Fish sauce, Annatto oil, Vegetables.', 'Cook noodles. Sauté seafood and vegetables. Mix with noodles and sauce. Top with more seafood.', 'https://www.todaysdelight.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/pancit-malabon-recipe-1724-500x500.jpg'),
('Dinuguan', 'A savory Filipino stew made from pork and pig''s blood.', 'Pork, Pig''s blood, Vinegar, Garlic, Chili peppers.', 'Sauté garlic and pork. Add pig''s blood and vinegar. Simmer until cooked.', 'https://assets.unileversolutions.com/recipes-v2/110821.jpg'),
('Mechado', 'A Filipino beef stew braised in a tomato-based sauce.', 'Beef, Tomato sauce, Soy sauce, Potatoes, Carrots.', 'Sear beef. Sauté vegetables. Simmer beef in tomato sauce until tender.', 'https://www.unileverfoodsolutions.com.ph/dam/global-ufs/mcos/SEA/calcmenu/recipes/PH-recipes/chicken-&-other-poultry-dishes/mechado-baka/mechado-baka-main-banner.jpg');
